name: Dantone | Grantham
description: In the rhythm of the big city restful sleep for many it has become a real luxury. That is why it is so important to spend these precious hours on a really high-quality furniture. Bed Grantham - truly royal bed, which will allow you to plunge into the serene realm of Morpheus. High headboard, nice texture, exclusive materials, and a huge choice of colors - with a bed every morning is good, and every dream - really sweet.
